      <strong>[Full name / company]</strong><br />
      [Street + number]<br />
      [Postcode + city]<br />
      Germany
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Phone: [phone number]<br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:info@about-berlin-hotels.de">info@about-berlin-hotels.de</a>
    </p>

    <h2>VAT ID</h2>
    <p>
      VAT identification number per § 27 a UStG:<br />
      [VAT-ID or „small business per § 19 UStG"]
    </p>

    <h2>Responsible for content per § 18 Abs. 2 MStV</h2>
    <p>
      [Full name]<br />
      [Address]
    </p>

    <h2>EU dispute resolution</h2>
